data.description: Welcome to your dream home in North Columbia, TN! This 5-bed, 3.5-bath, 2,688 sq. ft. gem in a charming subdivision offers a perfect blend of style and comfort. The open-concept living and dining areas, flooded with natural light, create a warm ambiance. A chef's dream, the gourmet kitchen features modern appliances and an inviting island. The master suite is a retreat with a spacious layout and a luxurious ensuite bath. The backyard is a haven for relaxation, ideal for outdoor activities. Additional features include a two-car garage and a dedicated laundry room. Located in North Columbia, TN, the property provides convenient access to local amenities. This modern, spacious, and well-located home is ready to welcome you. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours!
